items.title: "Hi to the fans, here is Osimhen. I'm happy to be in Morocco, and I can't wait for the start of AFCON. See you guys at the stadium. Ciao"

“My dream is for Bulgaria to be known worldwide not only for political or social issues but also as a cultural center. Our nation has been a spiritual cradle of Europe since ancient times, and we still have much to be proud of. My team and I will provide audiences with a world-class experience, as we do at Arena di Verona, the Metropolitan Opera in New York, Vienna, Rome, London, and elsewhere. I want Sofia to stand proudly alongside them”
